    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "JLPT N4 文法と文型例文 Grammar and Model Sentences – Nihongo-Pro.com",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Welcome to Nihongo-Pro",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "This textbook lists the 130 grammar patterns covered in Nihongo-Pro’s online JLPT",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "N4 Preparation class. These grammar patterns are used in everyday Japanese, so a firm",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "understanding of their use is essential not only for success on the Japanese Language",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Proficiency Test (JLPT), but also success in communicating in Japanese.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Japanese grammar presents challenges for any student of the language. The",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "meaning of a grammar form may not have an exact match in one’s own language, so it can",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "take extra work to learn and understand the exact meaning and the situations in which the",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "grammar form can be used.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "However, for most students, the hardest part about Japanese grammar isn’t in",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "learning the meaning of the grammar pattern itself—it’s in remembering the connective",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "tissue, i.e., how the grammar pattern connects with the rest of the sentence: Can I use a",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "noun here? Do I need to put a afterward? If I use a -adjective here, what comes after it?",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Practicing the correct use of the grammar pattern, including all the various",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "connectives, is a focus of Nihongo-Pro’s JLPT N4 Preparation class. We encourage you to",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "takes notes in this book (print a copy if needed) during your lessons and whenever you",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "study Japanese grammar.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "This book was made possible by the combined efforts of many individuals. All of the",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "examples in this book were prepared by Nihongo-Pro teachers, who worked untold hours to",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "produce the JLPT N4 curriculum and to write, check, and recheck the hundreds of model",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "sentences. I wish to thank Nami Hayashi, Yukiko Ishikawa, Fusayo Nagatomi, and Hiroko",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Yamafuji, who wrote dozens of the model sentences. Yutaka Aso and Yasuyo Sei wrote",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "dozens more, reviewed the JLPT N4 curriculum in its entirety, and added furigana to the",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "model sentences.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Finally, I wish to thank Michiko Lilly, who tirelessly dedicated her time throughout",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "the process, from producing all of our JLPT curricula and writing hundreds of model",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "sentences to orchestrating the efforts of the other contributors. I am deeply indebted to",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Michiko for her hard work.",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "I gratefully acknowledge the diligent support of all of these individuals in producing",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "this book and in making Nihongo-Pro’s JLPT classes a reality. I hope you benefit from this",
      "page": 3
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "book and our JLPT classes as much as we enjoy bringing them to you.",
